title: Norwegian psychedelic pop band Gold Celeste performs "The Dreamers" & more Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Gold Celeste performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded July 18, 2025.

Songs:
Time of Your Life 00:22
Open Your Eyes 4:00
The Dreamers 09:47
Grand New Spin 14:22

Simen Hallset - Bass, Vox
Eirik Fidjeland - Guitar, Vox
Peter Hiley - Guitar, Keys, Vox
Eirik Kirkemyr - Drums, Vox

Eric Werner - Percussion

Host: Jewel Loree

Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Ettie Wahl
